        "desc": "<p>卡布里埃商会会长，卡布里埃商会是刺玫会的兄弟组织。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyowiki/2023/12/08/4e904e9d971d9031fefc37f2cc034e9f_337902312346030853.png",
